1
00:00:23,550 --> 00:00:24,280
Master.

2
00:00:25,670 --> 00:00:26,530
Lejun is awake.

3
00:00:29,920 --> 00:00:31,550
Lejun told me a story,

4
00:00:32,470 --> 00:00:34,110
but it's too bizarre.

5
00:00:35,110 --> 00:00:36,310
It's hard to believe.

6
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,740
I hope you could clarify it for me.

7
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:41,920
Lejun said

8
00:00:43,110 --> 00:00:44,670
I'm not Prince Qi's son

9
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:48,640
but your son.

10
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:54,280
Is it true?

11
00:02:30,550 --> 00:02:34,710
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

12
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:37,670
[Episode 17]

13
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:52,470
Take a rest.

14
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:55,030
Have some ginseng soup
to strengthen your body.

15
00:02:55,030 --> 00:02:56,870
It'll be another tough few days.

16
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:58,760
Fortunately,

17
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:01,230
the ointment Ruisheng made works well.

18
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:03,430
The swelling has gone down a lot.

19
00:03:04,260 --> 00:03:06,520
How could the Grand Tutor bear to do this?

20
00:03:14,710 --> 00:03:15,400
And this.

21
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:18,240
Anmin asked me to bring this to you.

22
00:03:18,470 --> 00:03:20,360
He said he has nothing to offer

23
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,360
but an abundance of soft cushions

24
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,960
that can make sitting and kneeling

25
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,020
more comfortable.

26
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:26,750
Pad your knees with this.

27
00:03:27,079 --> 00:03:28,210
It'll ease the pain.

28
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,280
Don't worry.

29
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:34,490
Prince Jing'an's Mansion
will always be your home.

30
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:36,079
You can stay here

31
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:37,690
as long as you want.

32
00:03:51,870 --> 00:03:52,930
Thank you, Yuanji.

33
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,360
And Anmin too.

34
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,560
My Lady, it's cold at night.

35
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:04,810
Don't catch a cold.

36
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,560
Isn't this the fox fur cloak
His Highness hunted

37
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,030
and made himself a few years ago?

38
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:09,760
His Highness asked me to get it.

39
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,410
Why didn't he bring it himself?

40
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,300
And this ointment too.

41
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:20,720
He requested Ruisheng to

42
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,579
make it for you,

43
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:23,920
but he just won't come himself.

44
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:24,950
Maybe

45
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:27,310
he's afraid to see me.

46
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,270
What?

47
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:33,800
Nothing.

48
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:35,720
Yuanji,

49
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,960
I can keep watch here myself.

50
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,450
Please go back and rest.

51
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,740
Take care of yourself.

52
00:05:12,870 --> 00:05:17,070
When the Phoenix Heart Tokens appear,
peace shall be restored in the world.

53
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:19,160
How are the Phoenix Heart Tokens

54
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,490
linked to the minerals?

55
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:30,610
Your Highness,

56
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:32,870
I bought the pear blossom candy
from Chengyi Hall.

57
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:34,130
Deliver it to Lady Xie.

58
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:35,920
I heard she's been keeping vigil
for 3 days,

59
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:36,950
eaten or drunk nothing

60
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:38,409
except some ginseng soup.

61
00:05:38,430 --> 00:05:39,960
Aren't you going to see her?

62
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,070
Consort Yuanji and Madam Ruisheng

63
00:05:41,070 --> 00:05:42,000
visit her often.

64
00:05:42,270 --> 00:05:43,190
You're at least Lady Xie's

65
00:05:43,190 --> 00:05:44,120
husband in name,

66
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,530
and haven't divorced.

67
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,920
It's understandable for you to

68
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,310
observe mourning for her.

69
00:05:48,310 --> 00:05:50,310
I doubt she wants to see me right now.

70
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:52,290
Then this time,

71
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,130
shall I ask the Princess to deliver it?

72
00:05:57,310 --> 00:05:58,000
Hang on.

73
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:08,370
Your Highness.

74
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:14,130
Is she alright?

75
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:15,770
My Lady has fallen asleep.

76
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,080
Please keep your voice down.

77
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,910
My Lady finally fell asleep.

78
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,530
She'd been staying up for days.

79
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:33,560
Consort Yuanji and Madam Ruisheng were

80
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:35,159
worried that My Lady
couldn't endure the strain

81
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,620
so soon after her illness.

82
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:39,430
Consort Yuanji just
brought a bowl of calming soup

83
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:42,360
and tricked My Lady into drinking it
as ginseng soup.

84
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,240
Now she's finally asleep.

85
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:48,010
How can she sleep here?

86
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,190
I'll carry her back to rest.

87
00:06:51,190 --> 00:06:52,630
Back... Back where?

88
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,680
My Lady...

89
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:14,120
It seems the outcome of our bet
is decided.

90
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,410
I'm going to win.

91
00:07:16,430 --> 00:07:17,430
That's not right.

92
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:21,120
I remember betting that
they'd end up together.

93
00:07:21,260 --> 00:07:23,190
You always win bets with your husband

94
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:25,160
because you never own up
when you lose, right?

95
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,090
That's not true!

96
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:30,240
Fine, I'll let you have your way.

97
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,470
How about letting Ziqi study

98
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,430
both literature or medicine?

99
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,690
I think that's good.

100
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:37,350
By the way,

101
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:39,310
didn't you say His Highness
got injured

102
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:40,680
while getting bear gall

103
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,430
for Jiayu?

104
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:43,680
Can he carry someone now?

105
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:44,680
Don't worry.

106
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:46,250
He won't feel pain.

107
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:47,000
True.

108
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:50,920
Do you think Qing Long likes Yan Yue

109
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,950
or Nanxing?

110
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:53,750
I bet it's Yan Yue.

111
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:54,870
More bets?

112
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:31,530
♪ What's the cost
of going against the wind? ♪

113
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:36,039
♪ Knowing you, knowing me,
we live up to our promises ♪

114
00:08:36,059 --> 00:08:40,260
♪ Aligning the traces of our conviction ♪

115
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:42,850
♪ As long as I'm with you ♪

116
00:08:42,870 --> 00:08:45,850
♪ The journey can stretch on forever ♪

117
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:49,630
♪ Even if it puts my life on the line ♪

118
00:08:49,650 --> 00:08:52,340
♪ I shall never forget ♪

119
00:08:52,430 --> 00:08:56,820
♪ Let me dash toward where you are ♪

120
00:08:56,840 --> 00:09:00,270
♪ To seek out my own sanctuary ♪

121
00:09:00,300 --> 00:09:03,080
♪ Life hurries by, yet you alone ♪

122
00:09:03,110 --> 00:09:06,110
♪ Illuminate me
with your blazing radiance ♪

123
00:09:06,130 --> 00:09:10,180
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

124
00:09:10,210 --> 00:09:13,690
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

125
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:16,640
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

126
00:09:16,660 --> 00:09:22,190
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

127
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:10,880
This Phoenix Heart Token is
different from my mother's.

128
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:18,790
If it's not with him, then...

129
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,800
Why did you sigh with relief?

130
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:27,200
I don't have Her Highness's
Phoenix Heart Token.

131
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:29,730
I didn't kill Her Highness.
Someone else did.

132
00:10:30,270 --> 00:10:31,130
Who could it be?

133
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,560
Xie Jiayu, you're so smart.

134
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,780
You must already have an idea, right?

135
00:10:36,910 --> 00:10:37,570
Besides me,

136
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:38,840
of those by Her Highness's side,

137
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,970
who could do it and had a reason to do it?

138
00:10:41,790 --> 00:10:44,050
How many suspects are still in your list?

139
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:49,150
If not me, it must be her

140
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:50,630
or them.

141
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:54,600
You should be angry, furious,

142
00:10:54,910 --> 00:10:55,670
or confused.

143
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:58,280
So why did you sigh with relief?

144
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,800
You're relieved it isn't me,

145
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,550
aren't you?

146
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:11,200
Yaoyao,

147
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,910
why do you feel so?

148
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,270
Xiao Wuyi,

149
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:27,870
you're not completely in the clear yet.

150
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,960
Since you already knew my motive,

151
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,630
you could've hidden my mother's token

152
00:11:31,630 --> 00:11:32,560
somewhere else.

153
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:38,440
If you suspect it's me,

154
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:40,170
you can take my life at any time.

155
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:49,560
Do you think I dare not?

156
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,960
If I confess my love to you right now,

157
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:09,690
would you think I'm a lunatic?

158
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:13,840
You are a lunatic.

159
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:17,850
Xie Jiayu...

160
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:23,840
My heart belongs to you.

161
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:32,910
I know...

162
00:12:34,310 --> 00:12:36,530
♪ Weave our devotion
into a melody of two hearts ♪

163
00:12:34,550 --> 00:12:36,560
I know what Her Highness means to you.

164
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:38,850
♪ Mirror a gaze of stars and moon ♪

165
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:40,440
I'd never hurt the mother
of the woman I love.

166
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:42,830
♪ Forever illuminate each other's nights ♪

167
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:43,150
Never.

168
00:12:44,690 --> 00:12:47,210
♪ The truest, most profound affection ♪

169
00:12:47,230 --> 00:12:49,230
♪ An eternal vow ♪

170
00:12:49,630 --> 00:12:54,030
♪ To be each other's forever ♪

171
00:12:54,780 --> 00:12:59,080
♪ You enter my dreams,
permeating the crevices of my heart ♪

172
00:12:59,340 --> 00:13:01,340
♪ Every inch of longing ♪

173
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:05,080
♪ Tugs at unspeakable fantasies ♪

174
00:13:05,100 --> 00:13:09,210
♪ Know that your heart is my heart ♪

175
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,360
You're hurt?

176
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:11,830
♪ Cherishing each other ♪

177
00:13:09,870 --> 00:13:10,730
What happened?

178
00:13:11,270 --> 00:13:12,910
You didn't have this at Lingfeng Fort.

179
00:13:11,850 --> 00:13:16,440
♪ We will never be alone ♪

180
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:13,540
What...

181
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,600
♪ In the endless stream of time ♪

182
00:13:19,620 --> 00:13:22,460
♪ My life's every wish is for you ♪

183
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:27,440
♪ All the sweet nothings in the world
fall short ♪

184
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:29,960
♪ As time flows gently ♪

185
00:13:29,980 --> 00:13:32,600
♪ Hold each other and seal our vows ♪

186
00:13:32,620 --> 00:13:34,160
♪ Whatever the path ♪

187
00:13:34,180 --> 00:13:38,440
♪ I just want to be with you
for all time ♪

188
00:13:38,730 --> 00:13:40,320
♪ A lifelong promise ♪

189
00:13:40,350 --> 00:13:43,010
♪ My life's every moment is for you ♪

190
00:13:43,030 --> 00:13:45,030
♪ After all of it ♪

191
00:13:45,060 --> 00:13:47,880
♪ May all your dreams be realized ♪

192
00:13:48,910 --> 00:13:50,280
♪ Just you and me ♪

193
00:13:50,310 --> 00:13:53,490
♪ From dawn to dusk, year after year ♪

194
00:13:53,760 --> 00:13:59,640
♪ Hand in hand, let's experience
the bittersweet flavors of earthly life ♪

195
00:14:01,830 --> 00:14:12,290
♪ Hand in hand, let's experience
the bittersweet flavors of earthly life ♪

196
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:36,710
[Memorial tablet of
the late Princess Li Yunzhao]

197
00:14:34,030 --> 00:14:34,750
Mother,

198
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,790
if you're watching from heaven,

199
00:14:36,790 --> 00:14:37,910
please bless me

200
00:14:39,510 --> 00:14:40,910
to find the culprit soon.

201
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,370
Someone made a move.

202
00:14:49,040 --> 00:14:49,630
Who?

203
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:53,240
Silly brother, let's go see Father.

204
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:55,480
Yes, let's go see Father.

205
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:08,090
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

206
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:10,960
Memorials impeaching you

207
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,560
are flooding the Censorate.

208
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:14,740
Still won't hand Cui Jun over?

209
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:17,120
The prison cart is making its way.

210
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,960
It rained and there was a landslide.

211
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,510
Traveling on the mountain is slow.

212
00:15:20,510 --> 00:15:22,110
Don't give me that nonsense.

213
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:24,080
I've known that
Cui Jun had arrived in Jiankang.

214
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:25,670
He was just secretly imprisoned by you.

215
00:15:25,670 --> 00:15:27,130
Even if I hand over Cui Jun,

216
00:15:27,390 --> 00:15:29,790
the nobles won't try to
impeach me any less.

217
00:15:31,390 --> 00:15:33,240
You're just a witness
in the Cui Family Case,

218
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:35,000
escorting the Cui prisoners on the way.

219
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,000
Once in Jiankang,

220
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:38,120
you have to hand them over
to the Court of Judicial Review.

221
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:40,030
Do you really want to
pocket the Phoenix Heart Token

222
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:41,760
and the Cui family's minerals?

223
00:15:42,630 --> 00:15:45,960
Did Her Highness's death
really have nothing to do with you?

224
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:48,120
Seriously?

225
00:15:51,030 --> 00:15:52,230
It's not what I think.

226
00:15:52,510 --> 00:15:55,000
It's a rumor in the court,

227
00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:58,240
saying Her Highness's death
wasn't an accident,

228
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,670
but that you murdered her

229
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:00,730
to seize her token.

230
00:16:01,510 --> 00:16:03,170
If you don't hand over Cui Jun,

231
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:04,840
the rumors will just worsen

232
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:06,120
with each passing day.

233
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,910
The nobles are watching you like a hawk,

234
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:09,970
hoping to catch you slip up in any way.

235
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,750
Cui Jun hasn't confessed

236
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:13,010
how to crack the token,

237
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:14,690
so I can't hand him over.

238
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:16,550
Yan Yue said that be it Zhuyou hypnosis,

239
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:17,670
poison, or torture,

240
00:16:17,670 --> 00:16:18,800
he didn't say a word.

241
00:16:19,270 --> 00:16:21,550
The spy trained by
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin

242
00:16:21,550 --> 00:16:22,810
is indeed a character.

243
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:26,320
Why is it you reporting this?
Where's Yan Yue?

244
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:29,920
What's wrong?

245
00:16:47,630 --> 00:16:48,490
Your Highness.

246
00:16:49,360 --> 00:16:50,290
What's going on?

247
00:16:51,630 --> 00:16:53,390
Lady Xie said she wants to
work on her martial arts,

248
00:16:53,390 --> 00:16:55,590
that mourning is no reason to slack off.

249
00:16:55,790 --> 00:16:57,520
What did she eat for breakfast?

250
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:58,490
Nothing.

251
00:16:59,390 --> 00:17:00,270
Lady Xie heard that

252
00:17:00,270 --> 00:17:02,120
you do it on an empty stomach
early in the morning,

253
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:03,120
and insisted on doing the same.

254
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:03,720
Nonsense!

255
00:17:07,589 --> 00:17:08,109
Jiayu!

256
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:09,750
Jiayu.

257
00:17:11,109 --> 00:17:13,109
Trying to starve yourself to death?

258
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:16,819
What happened?

259
00:17:18,560 --> 00:17:19,480
Nothing.

260
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:26,560
Have this.

261
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:38,170
Learning martial arts takes time.

262
00:17:38,510 --> 00:17:40,170
It's good if you want to train.

263
00:17:40,590 --> 00:17:42,350
But you have to take it step by step,

264
00:17:42,350 --> 00:17:44,350
instead of rushing it, understand?

265
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:46,300
I just want to have something to do

266
00:17:47,280 --> 00:17:48,740
so my mind can stop racing.

267
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:50,680
Xie Jiayu.

268
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:56,040
Stop mistreating yourself.

269
00:17:59,780 --> 00:18:01,640
You said your heart belongs to me.

270
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:03,920
Then would you

271
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:06,260
kill for me as well?

272
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,830
Princess Yunzhao just passed away.

273
00:18:08,830 --> 00:18:11,030
But if you can't pull yourself together,

274
00:18:11,030 --> 00:18:13,490
no one else can be
responsible for your life.

275
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:15,750
Not even you?

276
00:18:17,290 --> 00:18:18,440
I can kill for you.

277
00:18:20,130 --> 00:18:22,590
But I can't help you
overcome this obstacle.

278
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,510
You already know who did it,

279
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:27,480
don't you?

280
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:33,750
Bad news, Your Highness!

281
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:35,460
Cui Jun was taken away!

282
00:18:37,590 --> 00:18:38,200
What?

283
00:18:38,350 --> 00:18:41,440
The kidnapper left a message on the wall,
saying they were

284
00:18:41,440 --> 00:18:43,640
acting on Crown Prince Wenxi's orders.

285
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:44,370
Impossible.

286
00:18:45,670 --> 00:18:47,530
Don't go out for the next few days,

287
00:18:47,550 --> 00:18:48,240
OK?

288
00:19:06,880 --> 00:19:07,480
My Lady.

289
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:10,210
The Heir arranged all this.

290
00:19:11,750 --> 00:19:14,550
He said although you're
not a real married couple,

291
00:19:14,640 --> 00:19:15,970
etiquette comes first.

292
00:19:16,070 --> 00:19:18,160
Princess Yunzhao is considered
half an elder to him.

293
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,160
For the mourning,

294
00:19:19,270 --> 00:19:21,160
the estate should show its respects.

295
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:23,360
The entire estate will mourn
by wearing

296
00:19:23,640 --> 00:19:24,700
mourning clothes.

297
00:19:24,750 --> 00:19:26,070
We've reported this
to the Dowager Princess,

298
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:27,130
and she has agreed.

299
00:19:27,510 --> 00:19:28,400
I just wonder

300
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:30,200
why the Heir took so long to

301
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:31,960
show this sincerity.

302
00:19:33,720 --> 00:19:35,920
He was afraid I wouldn't like it before.

303
00:19:36,440 --> 00:19:38,310
But he's not afraid now?

304
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:42,290
My heart belongs to you.

305
00:19:44,170 --> 00:19:46,100
My Lady, I don't think

306
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:47,480
the Heir did it.

307
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:49,000
I know he didn't do it.

308
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:51,150
Someone wants me to think

309
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:53,770
he killed her for her Phoenix Heart Token.

310
00:19:54,030 --> 00:19:56,490
Crown Prince Wenxi is
the hope of the people.

311
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:58,790
Now that the token has appeared,

312
00:19:58,790 --> 00:20:01,790
Crown Prince Wenxi
should naturally reveal himself.

313
00:20:03,940 --> 00:20:05,670
Lejun, what are you doing here?

314
00:20:08,170 --> 00:20:10,300
I was just about to call you for dinner.

315
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:12,640
I lost my earring,

316
00:20:13,110 --> 00:20:14,720
so I came out to look for it.

317
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:19,590
Did you find it?

318
00:20:24,180 --> 00:20:24,900
But

319
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,110
Xiao Wuyi and my mother are

320
00:20:26,110 --> 00:20:27,970
indeed hiding something from me.

321
00:20:28,070 --> 00:20:29,270
And my mother's death

322
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:30,850
is related to it.

323
00:20:43,600 --> 00:20:46,750
It all started
because of Crown Prince Wenxi.

324
00:20:47,670 --> 00:20:50,290
[Memorial tablet of
the late Princess Li Yunzhao]

325
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:56,590
Xie, why are you here?

326
00:20:57,360 --> 00:20:58,220
Your Highness.

327
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:02,070
You agreed to let the entire estate

328
00:21:02,070 --> 00:21:03,200
mourn for my mother.

329
00:21:03,310 --> 00:21:04,070
I should

330
00:21:04,270 --> 00:21:05,400
thank you in person.

331
00:21:05,510 --> 00:21:06,910
It's the least I could do.

332
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:09,510
Nanxing, take the things inside.

333
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:10,680
Yes.

334
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:18,210
Your Highness,

335
00:21:18,550 --> 00:21:20,160
you're also from the Capital.

336
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:21,720
There are some things about the past

337
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:22,920
that I want to ask you.

338
00:21:23,240 --> 00:21:23,960
Go ahead.

339
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:25,270
I heard that my mother

340
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:27,400
used to be very close to Empress Wenxi;

341
00:21:27,790 --> 00:21:28,920
close like sisters.

342
00:21:30,070 --> 00:21:30,680
Yes.

343
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,830
The Two Beauties of the Capital

344
00:21:33,830 --> 00:21:35,160
referred to Empress Wenxi

345
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,420
and Princess Yunzhao.

346
00:21:36,830 --> 00:21:37,920
I also heard

347
00:21:38,240 --> 00:21:39,270
that Old General Xiao

348
00:21:39,270 --> 00:21:42,160
used to be a groom
for Empress Wenxi's maternal family.

349
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:44,880
He entered the Imperial Guard
because of Empress Wenxi's recommendation,

350
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:46,030
and later led the Imperial Guard

351
00:21:46,030 --> 00:21:48,560
to escort the Ye royals and nobles
to the south

352
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:50,110
Establishing Southern Ye

353
00:21:50,110 --> 00:21:51,350
and assisting the emperor,

354
00:21:51,350 --> 00:21:53,010
he was titled Prince Jing'an.

355
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:55,070
That is true.

356
00:21:55,750 --> 00:21:56,550
But why didn't

357
00:21:56,550 --> 00:21:58,680
my mother ever mention the Xiao family

358
00:21:59,110 --> 00:22:00,880
or Old General Xiao to me?

359
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:07,240
They were of different social classes.

360
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:10,070
Not to mention the Prince
was just a groom back then.

361
00:22:10,070 --> 00:22:11,270
It's no surprise that

362
00:22:11,350 --> 00:22:13,200
the Princess didn't remember him.

363
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:15,750
But Empress Wenxi could
entrust her last 50,000 Imperial Guards

364
00:22:15,750 --> 00:22:17,400
to Old General Xiao,
so he must've been

365
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:18,600
a trusted confidant.

366
00:22:19,790 --> 00:22:22,590
My mother was also
someone Empress Wenxi trusted.

367
00:22:23,830 --> 00:22:25,360
How could she not remember?

368
00:22:27,310 --> 00:22:30,680
When Empress Wenxi gave birth
to the Crown Prince on the brink of death,

369
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:32,030
for some unknown reason,

370
00:22:32,030 --> 00:22:34,160
the Crown Prince failed to appear
for a long time.

371
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,920
So, the court was
divided into two factions.

372
00:22:35,920 --> 00:22:38,240
One faction insisted on
waiting for the Crown Prince to return

373
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:39,830
and supporting the orthodox heir,

374
00:22:39,830 --> 00:22:40,960
such as your mother.

375
00:22:41,750 --> 00:22:43,790
The other faction was the various nobles,

376
00:22:43,790 --> 00:22:45,960
who advocated choosing
a prince of similar age

377
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:47,550
from the royal clans

378
00:22:47,550 --> 00:22:49,010
and supporting him first.

379
00:22:49,030 --> 00:22:50,960
The two factions were deadlocked.

380
00:22:51,030 --> 00:22:52,590
Only Prince Jing'an,
who commanded the Imperial Guard,

381
00:22:52,590 --> 00:22:53,920
had the right to decide.

382
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:55,970
The Prince chose the nobles

383
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:57,530
and supported Emperor Rui,

384
00:22:57,590 --> 00:23:00,110
who is His Majesty's father.

385
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:02,200
Yes.

386
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:03,830
Since then,

387
00:23:04,030 --> 00:23:06,960
the Princess and the Xiao family
have had no contact.

388
00:23:07,310 --> 00:23:10,110
Then didn't the Prince
have a Phoenix Heart Token?

389
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:16,920
I was just asking.

390
00:23:17,750 --> 00:23:18,440
Well...

391
00:23:19,310 --> 00:23:20,970
My mother's token is missing.

392
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:23,510
Some say Xiao Wuyi killed my mother

393
00:23:25,750 --> 00:23:28,310
for her Phoenix Heart Token.

394
00:23:28,540 --> 00:23:29,210
That's why...

395
00:23:29,210 --> 00:23:29,940
Impossible.

396
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:32,350
I can guarantee you that.

397
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:34,980
Xiao Wuyi would never kill the Princess.

398
00:23:37,640 --> 00:23:38,500
He couldn't...

399
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:48,020
Please believe me.

400
00:23:48,550 --> 00:23:50,550
Wuyi would never kill the Princess.

401
00:23:51,640 --> 00:23:52,770
You must trust Wuyi.

402
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:54,540
Don't let others mislead you.

403
00:23:56,550 --> 00:23:57,510
I understand.

404
00:23:59,510 --> 00:24:01,590
If you say so, I believe you.

405
00:24:03,110 --> 00:24:04,110
I trust Xiao Wuyi.

406
00:24:12,350 --> 00:24:13,000
Lady Xie,

407
00:24:13,480 --> 00:24:14,280
please tell me

408
00:24:15,070 --> 00:24:16,670
why you're bringing me here.

409
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,160
Didn't I help you get

410
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:20,000
the chance to compete in archery?

411
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:21,310
You said you owed me a favor

412
00:24:21,310 --> 00:24:22,910
and would do one thing for me.

413
00:24:24,400 --> 00:24:25,240
I did say that.

414
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:26,650
Then ask no more.

415
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:28,960
I promise this matter

416
00:24:29,310 --> 00:24:31,040
doesn't violate the laws of Ye.

417
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,880
Sir, here he is.

418
00:24:36,590 --> 00:24:38,050
Please hold out your hand.

419
00:24:59,550 --> 00:25:00,110
No.

420
00:25:02,890 --> 00:25:03,750
Thank you, sir.

421
00:25:04,110 --> 00:25:06,070
What exactly is going on?

422
00:25:06,510 --> 00:25:07,350
"No" what?

423
00:25:10,830 --> 00:25:11,480
Wuyi?

424
00:25:19,030 --> 00:25:19,750
You drew me.

425
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:22,980
When was this? At the martial arts arena?

426
00:25:24,350 --> 00:25:25,480
The bone reader said

427
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:28,170
you and Xiao Yao
aren't biological brothers.

428
00:25:28,270 --> 00:25:29,110
So sure, huh?

429
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:30,810
What if he was wrong?

430
00:25:31,110 --> 00:25:32,590
The fact that you're sitting here

431
00:25:32,590 --> 00:25:33,880
proves that I'm right.

432
00:25:36,400 --> 00:25:37,070
When did you

433
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:38,670
start doubting my identity?

434
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:40,480
At Lingfeng Fort.

435
00:25:40,790 --> 00:25:41,450
That early?

436
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:43,720
At first,

437
00:25:44,310 --> 00:25:46,160
I didn't care who Crown Prince Wenxi was.

438
00:25:46,160 --> 00:25:47,160
I only cared about

439
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:48,530
who murdered my mother.

440
00:25:49,070 --> 00:25:50,480
I know my mother told you

441
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:53,410
she'd trade the token for my freedom.

442
00:25:54,110 --> 00:25:55,570
The night before she died,

443
00:25:56,200 --> 00:25:57,510
I saw you two arguing.

444
00:25:58,440 --> 00:25:59,170
She wouldn't

445
00:25:59,510 --> 00:26:00,240
give this token

446
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:02,500
to anyone other than Crown Prince Wenxi.

447
00:26:03,650 --> 00:26:04,980
Since she promised you,

448
00:26:05,350 --> 00:26:07,150
how could she go back on her word?

449
00:26:07,310 --> 00:26:08,710
That's why you suspected

450
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:12,190
that I was the one
who attacked Her Highness

451
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:13,350
to get the token?

452
00:26:14,350 --> 00:26:15,080
Besides you,

453
00:26:16,030 --> 00:26:17,960
Lejun was also a probable suspect.

454
00:26:18,070 --> 00:26:18,640
That day,

455
00:26:19,310 --> 00:26:21,550
I heard Her Highness arguing with someone.

456
00:26:21,550 --> 00:26:23,960
She said she knew the whereabouts
of Crown Prince Wenxi.

457
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:25,620
She was going to give the token

458
00:26:26,110 --> 00:26:27,510
to Crown Prince Wenxi.

459
00:26:28,280 --> 00:26:29,610
In the carriage,

460
00:26:30,590 --> 00:26:32,880
I did give her a chance.

461
00:26:33,230 --> 00:26:34,830
But she knew your background

462
00:26:35,400 --> 00:26:38,860
and insisted on helping
Crown Prince Wenxi ascend the throne.

463
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:40,240
If she heard my mother's desire

464
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:42,110
to support Crown Prince Wenxi's ascension,

465
00:26:42,110 --> 00:26:44,170
it'd pose a threat to Mao's position.

466
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:46,900
So she also had a reason
to take the token.

467
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:48,810
Once Crown Prince Wenxi

468
00:26:49,030 --> 00:26:51,030
returns to Jiankang with the token,

469
00:26:51,590 --> 00:26:53,200
what will you do, Brother?

470
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:55,210
For the Eastern Palace,

471
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:57,070
you even gave up Yaoyao.

472
00:26:57,240 --> 00:26:59,440
I had to get rid of the ticking time bomb!

473
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,790
Without Her Highness's token,

474
00:27:06,510 --> 00:27:08,400
even if Crown Prince Wenxi comes,

475
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:12,200
the prophecy is considered broken.

476
00:27:13,590 --> 00:27:14,990
Who was she arguing with?

477
00:27:16,230 --> 00:27:18,640
I didn't see clearly, but I think...

478
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:21,050
it must be Xiao Wuyi.

479
00:27:21,590 --> 00:27:23,450
Xiao Wuyi really wants the token.

480
00:27:23,880 --> 00:27:26,880
He's been holding on to Cui Jun's token.

481
00:27:27,510 --> 00:27:28,110
Brother.

482
00:27:29,160 --> 00:27:30,000
In my opinion,

483
00:27:30,550 --> 00:27:31,750
to Xiao Wuyi,

484
00:27:32,550 --> 00:27:35,000
you're just a pawn
kept in the imperial government

485
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:36,800
to facilitate the Beifu Reform.

486
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:39,830
If he dares to fall in love with Yaoyao,

487
00:27:40,550 --> 00:27:41,610
how much affection

488
00:27:42,110 --> 00:27:43,720
does he have left for you?

489
00:27:50,680 --> 00:27:51,680
You must never...

490
00:27:53,830 --> 00:27:55,200
trust Xiao Wuyi again.

491
00:27:58,590 --> 00:28:00,450
Only you have the grain that could

492
00:28:00,510 --> 00:28:01,510
drive a horse mad.

493
00:28:02,030 --> 00:28:02,920
So at first,

494
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:05,840
I was more suspicious of you.

495
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:08,160
When did it change?

496
00:28:16,550 --> 00:28:17,350
On the day of the wedding,

497
00:28:17,010 --> 00:28:19,050
[Ye Xing, a Shadow Envoy]

498
00:28:17,530 --> 00:28:19,530
the one who died was my twin brother.

499
00:28:19,560 --> 00:28:20,510
My brother and I were

500
00:28:20,510 --> 00:28:22,910
secret guards raised by Princess Yunzhao.

501
00:28:24,310 --> 00:28:25,510
Up until the wedding,

502
00:28:25,750 --> 00:28:26,750
our existence was

503
00:28:26,830 --> 00:28:28,630
unknown even to the Grand Tutor.

504
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:36,960
Aren't you dead?

505
00:28:38,590 --> 00:28:40,160
Before Mother went to Lingfeng Fort,

506
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:41,560
she sent him on an errand.

507
00:28:42,030 --> 00:28:43,550
But by the time he returned,

508
00:28:43,550 --> 00:28:45,080
Mother was already killed.

509
00:28:45,110 --> 00:28:47,330
When we entered the city that day,
I stayed behind

510
00:28:47,330 --> 00:28:48,590
just to tell Li Mao that

511
00:28:49,670 --> 00:28:50,870
I've found a witness.

512
00:28:51,830 --> 00:28:53,440
Lejun is severely injured and unconscious.

513
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:54,480
If she wakes up,

514
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:56,380
ask her to think carefully

515
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:58,740
if there are any other witness clues.

516
00:28:59,510 --> 00:29:01,840
I had someone look for the groom's family,

517
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:04,060
hoping to find some new clues.

518
00:29:04,340 --> 00:29:05,070
Then, My Lady

519
00:29:05,510 --> 00:29:06,790
ordered me to immediately take control

520
00:29:06,790 --> 00:29:07,880
of the groom's family

521
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:09,030
and bring them to Jiankang,

522
00:29:09,030 --> 00:29:09,720
to see if anyone

523
00:29:09,720 --> 00:29:11,650
would take the opportunity to act.

524
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:13,830
As expected, Prince Qi's men came.

525
00:29:15,190 --> 00:29:17,270
So you suspected Li Lejun early on.

526
00:29:18,030 --> 00:29:19,090
They took the bait.

527
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:21,820
I just cast the hook for everyone.

528
00:29:22,590 --> 00:29:24,000
Luring the snake out of its hole

529
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,260
also alerts the snake.

530
00:29:25,510 --> 00:29:26,590
Li Mao and Li Lejun

531
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:28,680
must've noticed your suspicion,

532
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:30,070
and will soon find out that

533
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:30,750
the groom's family

534
00:29:30,750 --> 00:29:32,010
actually know nothing

535
00:29:32,510 --> 00:29:33,770
and aren't witnesses.

536
00:29:34,200 --> 00:29:35,440
So what if they know?

537
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:42,200
Alright.

538
00:29:43,310 --> 00:29:44,340
Then let's talk about me.

539
00:29:44,340 --> 00:29:46,340
When exactly did I give myself away?

540
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:51,680
When Cui Jun took my mother hostage.

541
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:54,030
Crown Prince Wenxi died long ago!

542
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:55,000
He didn't die!

543
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,610
Cui Jun was taken away.

544
00:29:58,640 --> 00:30:00,960
The kidnapper left a message on the wall,
saying they were

545
00:30:00,960 --> 00:30:03,000
acting on Crown Prince Wenxi's orders.

546
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:03,730
Impossible.

547
00:30:07,110 --> 00:30:08,440
Being overly certain is

548
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:10,530
indeed inappropriate.

549
00:30:10,750 --> 00:30:12,080
Once suspicion arises,

550
00:30:12,590 --> 00:30:13,650
it can't be curbed.

551
00:30:14,510 --> 00:30:16,070
Xiyue Restaurant keeps telling stories

552
00:30:16,070 --> 00:30:17,830
about the token and Crown Prince Wenxi.

553
00:30:17,830 --> 00:30:19,400
If Crown Prince Wenxi is really alive,

554
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:20,460
how old would he be?

555
00:30:20,590 --> 00:30:22,830
Twenty-four years ago... So, 24.

556
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:26,880
The Dowager Princess's
contradictory attitude towards you...

557
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:28,070
Wuyi is also my son.

558
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:31,520
Then why refuse to go see Xiao Wuyi?

559
00:30:32,150 --> 00:30:34,410
Xiao Wuyi would never kill the Princess.

560
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:37,370
And Mother's blind trust in you

561
00:30:37,750 --> 00:30:39,240
when she was at the Cui Mansion.

562
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:40,570
Who says we stand alone?

563
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:41,920
We share weal and woe.

564
00:30:42,510 --> 00:30:43,400
He indeed

565
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:45,060
gave himself a very nice name.

566
00:30:48,510 --> 00:30:49,160
Also,

567
00:30:51,030 --> 00:30:53,160
her evaluation of Crown Prince Wenxi.

568
00:30:53,530 --> 00:30:55,070
Mother said Crown Prince Wenxi is

569
00:30:55,070 --> 00:30:56,510
someone who values the world

570
00:30:56,510 --> 00:30:57,720
more than himself,

571
00:30:57,880 --> 00:31:00,000
who spares no effort for this world,

572
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:02,350
and that those who can bear this saying

573
00:31:02,350 --> 00:31:03,720
are few in this world.

574
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:07,720
I happen to know

575
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:09,970
a lunatic of such a caliber.

576
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:13,440
Xie Jiayu,

577
00:31:14,590 --> 00:31:16,590
so you have such a high opinion of me.

578
00:31:17,270 --> 00:31:18,070
Xiao Wuyi,

579
00:31:19,080 --> 00:31:21,280
it's time to reveal your true identity.

580
00:31:23,270 --> 00:31:23,880
Yes.

581
00:31:26,890 --> 00:31:28,520
I am Crown Prince Wenxi.

582
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:34,870
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

583
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:43,170
It's time to bring Mother home.

584
00:31:43,790 --> 00:31:46,450
Nanxing, help me with
my grooming and dressing.

585
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:52,960
Over the years,

586
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:55,920
my Xie family had received so much favor
from the Princess.

587
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:57,050
My Shanji Hall could

588
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:58,790
stay open thanks to the Princess's

589
00:31:58,790 --> 00:32:00,270
years of financial support.

590
00:32:00,270 --> 00:32:01,550
These Buddhist scriptures were

591
00:32:01,550 --> 00:32:02,720
hand-copied by the women and children

592
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:04,320
of Shanji Hall these few days

593
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:06,000
to be offered to the Princess.

594
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:07,440
Offer condolences!

595
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:11,520
Princess Pingning has arrived.

596
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,730
Greetings, Your Highness.

597
00:32:24,610 --> 00:32:27,090
My brother and I've had a tough life.

598
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:30,010
Thankfully, the Princess took care of us.

599
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:32,210
We're forever indebted to her.

600
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:33,800
I have requested a decree

601
00:32:34,310 --> 00:32:36,110
to be an escort for the Princess.

602
00:32:53,110 --> 00:32:54,510
Greetings, Grand Tutor.

603
00:32:58,680 --> 00:33:00,740
Doing this even when you're injured.

604
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:03,130
This is very thoughtful of you.

605
00:33:15,440 --> 00:33:16,720
It's time!

606
00:33:17,110 --> 00:33:19,720
Start the procession! Break the bowl!

607
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:24,550
Wait!

608
00:33:37,750 --> 00:33:38,440
Father,

609
00:33:39,200 --> 00:33:40,060
with me around,

610
00:33:40,590 --> 00:33:42,320
how can my cousin break the bowl

611
00:33:42,530 --> 00:33:44,190
and an outsider be the escort?

612
00:33:51,640 --> 00:33:53,900
Lejun fell down the cliff with my mother,

613
00:33:54,440 --> 00:33:56,100
yet she recovered so quickly.

614
00:33:58,310 --> 00:33:59,070
It seems

615
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:01,550
you're very blessed.

616
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:04,920
Yaoyao, I'm sorry.

617
00:34:05,480 --> 00:34:07,280
I didn't hold onto the Princess.

618
00:34:07,480 --> 00:34:10,280
If only I had moved faster that day.

619
00:34:10,710 --> 00:34:12,590
Yaoyao, where have you been?

620
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:14,400
It's been past the 7 days of mourning,

621
00:34:14,400 --> 00:34:16,550
and you haven't been
kneeling by the coffin.

622
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:18,010
I forbade her from coming.

623
00:34:18,280 --> 00:34:20,050
I thought I made it very clear last time

624
00:34:20,050 --> 00:34:23,050
that you're not allowed to
set foot in the Xie Mansion!

625
00:34:37,150 --> 00:34:38,679
Everyone, you may not know,

626
00:34:39,070 --> 00:34:41,130
but my mother had divorced my father.

627
00:34:43,670 --> 00:34:44,710
Mother wouldn't want...

628
00:34:44,710 --> 00:34:45,190
Divorced?

629
00:34:45,190 --> 00:34:47,650
To be buried
in the Xie ancestral graveyard.

630
00:34:48,110 --> 00:34:49,030
So today,

631
00:34:50,190 --> 00:34:51,280
I'm here to take her away.

632
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:52,080
How insolent!

633
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:53,000
Jiayu,

634
00:34:53,480 --> 00:34:54,960
you can't just spout nonsense.

635
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:56,960
How could your parents be divorced?

636
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:58,560
I have two letters in my hand.

637
00:34:59,590 --> 00:35:00,450
This letter was

638
00:35:01,110 --> 00:35:03,480
written to me by my mother
when she left Jiankang.

639
00:35:03,480 --> 00:35:05,340
She said she'd divorced my father

640
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,670
and wanted to go out to relax

641
00:35:06,670 --> 00:35:07,870
and travel the world.

642
00:35:08,230 --> 00:35:09,430
The second letter...

643
00:35:11,510 --> 00:35:12,760
was written to my father
when my mother was

644
00:35:12,760 --> 00:35:13,760
at Lingfeng Fort.

645
00:35:15,070 --> 00:35:17,200
These are the Princess's belongings.

646
00:35:20,460 --> 00:35:22,060
Unfortunately, she died

647
00:35:22,920 --> 00:35:24,320
before she could mail it.

648
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,000
Father,

649
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:28,060
want to take a look?

650
00:35:28,510 --> 00:35:29,550
No need.

651
00:35:31,590 --> 00:35:33,440
My marriage to your mother

652
00:35:34,110 --> 00:35:35,670
was decreed by the royals.

653
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:39,070
So, without verification of the Clan Court

654
00:35:39,070 --> 00:35:40,360
and the approval of the Inner Court,

655
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:41,710
your divorce paper is

656
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:44,280
utterly invalid.

657
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:47,960
Since the entire Xie family
is gathered here today,

658
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:49,280
I will say it again:

659
00:35:50,990 --> 00:35:53,850
Xie Jiayu is not
Yunzhao's and my biological child!

660
00:35:55,150 --> 00:35:56,630
-What?
-What?

661
00:35:56,880 --> 00:35:57,900
-What's this?
-I don't know.

662
00:35:57,900 --> 00:35:59,130
She is just

663
00:35:59,880 --> 00:36:02,340
an orphan
Yunzhao picked up from somewhere.

664
00:36:03,320 --> 00:36:04,030
A little pet

665
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:06,360
kept by Yunzhao for just over a decade.

666
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:08,920
So, what right...

667
00:36:10,880 --> 00:36:12,210
What right does she have

668
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:15,330
to make decisions for
my Xie family and Yunzhao?

669
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:17,140
Let's not waste any more time.

670
00:36:19,110 --> 00:36:19,800
T-This...

671
00:36:34,360 --> 00:36:37,420
Did Prince Jing'an's Mansion
raise a bunch of bandits?

672
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:39,630
Barging into my Xie mourning hall

673
00:36:39,630 --> 00:36:41,090
to snatch the coffin, huh?

674
00:36:41,590 --> 00:36:42,070
Is there

675
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,230
still any law and order?

676
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:45,530
Grand Tutor.

677
00:36:46,760 --> 00:36:48,030
Xie Jiayu's word is law

678
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:49,280
today.

679
00:36:51,590 --> 00:36:54,320
I hope you can let Jiayu
finish what she has to say.

680
00:37:02,150 --> 00:37:04,280
Cui Jun is a secret spy of Northern Qin.

681
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:05,960
After Mother was controlled by him,

682
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:07,420
she had a chance to escape.

683
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:10,590
But she heard Cui Jun
mention the An-Lu case.

684
00:37:10,590 --> 00:37:11,840
To pry the truth

685
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:12,880
out of Cui Jun,

686
00:37:13,320 --> 00:37:15,520
Mother spared no effort to deal with him

687
00:37:15,760 --> 00:37:17,420
and almost couldn't get away.

688
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:19,290
Mother knew that

689
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:21,930
the An-Lu case was
a lifelong emotional burden of yours.

690
00:37:21,930 --> 00:37:23,600
You need closure.

691
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:26,440
So she'd rather risk her life

692
00:37:27,280 --> 00:37:28,940
just to seek the truth for you.

693
00:37:29,760 --> 00:37:30,890
Mother once thought

694
00:37:31,030 --> 00:37:32,830
your obsessions were all wrong.

695
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:36,400
Only later did she know she was wrong too.

696
00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:38,070
Now,

697
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:41,770
the truth is in my hands.

698
00:37:49,110 --> 00:37:49,630
Yaoyao!

699
00:37:50,400 --> 00:37:50,800
Don't!

700
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:53,650
Grand Tutor!

701
00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:55,150
I said to

702
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,860
let Xie Jiayu finish speaking today.

703
00:38:02,150 --> 00:38:02,800
Father.

704
00:38:04,110 --> 00:38:05,510
My mother was murdered.

705
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:08,150
Do you dare to let me investigate

706
00:38:08,150 --> 00:38:09,880
who really murdered my mother?

707
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:16,280
Xie Jiayu, the nerve of you to say this.

708
00:38:17,320 --> 00:38:18,670
It was clearly because
the horse got spooked

709
00:38:18,670 --> 00:38:20,230
that your mother had that accidental fall.

710
00:38:20,230 --> 00:38:21,670
If you hadn't swapped carriages with her,

711
00:38:21,670 --> 00:38:23,360
it would've been you instead.

712
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:24,760
What else is there to investigate?

713
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:26,070
Fine, I understand.

714
00:38:27,480 --> 00:38:29,340
If you don't want to investigate,

715
00:38:30,670 --> 00:38:31,670
I'll do it myself.

716
00:38:33,070 --> 00:38:34,800
I'll get justice for my mother.

717
00:38:42,380 --> 00:38:43,980
Let me ask you again, Father.

718
00:38:44,030 --> 00:38:46,630
If I want to exchange the An-Lu case
for Mother,

719
00:38:47,110 --> 00:38:48,770
will you make the trade or not?

720
00:38:48,860 --> 00:38:50,410
No, no, you...

721
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,110
Father.

722
00:38:52,010 --> 00:38:54,570
Will you make the trade or not?

723
00:39:02,110 --> 00:39:03,240
No! Don't, don't!

724
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:07,030
If there's any truth
to the An-Lu case,

725
00:39:07,030 --> 00:39:09,230
then that's a matter of state!

726
00:39:09,800 --> 00:39:12,670
How can you jeopardize the state

727
00:39:13,150 --> 00:39:14,950
for your own selfish interests?

728
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:16,080
Is that so?

729
00:39:17,230 --> 00:39:17,960
Then Father,

730
00:39:18,590 --> 00:39:20,070
in the repeating crossbow case,

731
00:39:20,070 --> 00:39:21,760
didn't you jeopardize the state

732
00:39:21,760 --> 00:39:22,880
for your own selfish interests?

733
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:23,630
Nonsense!

734
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:26,920
What does your father have to do
with the repeating crossbow?

735
00:39:26,920 --> 00:39:28,440
Whether I'm speaking nonsense,

736
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:29,670
Father knows best.

737
00:39:30,210 --> 00:39:32,070
Whether I want to
burn everything down with me,

738
00:39:32,070 --> 00:39:33,400
Father also knows best.

739
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:36,590
Mother told me

740
00:39:36,590 --> 00:39:37,800
your past stories.

741
00:39:40,710 --> 00:39:42,510
Since you love someone else,

742
00:39:43,110 --> 00:39:45,310
since even the beginning was a mistake,

743
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:47,620
then why wouldn't you let Mother be free?

744
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:54,460
From the Capital to Jiankang,

745
00:39:55,230 --> 00:39:56,290
too many people are

746
00:39:56,630 --> 00:39:58,630
trapped in the past and in the court.

747
00:39:59,150 --> 00:40:00,400
Mother is gone.

748
00:40:02,190 --> 00:40:03,070
I just want her

749
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:04,800
to find peace in the afterlife.

750
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:07,760
How could you—how could anyone—

751
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:10,000
understand my love for Yunzhao?

752
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:12,710
She was the one

753
00:40:13,070 --> 00:40:14,840
who chose the wrong beginning.

754
00:40:15,230 --> 00:40:15,960
Since it was wrong,

755
00:40:15,960 --> 00:40:17,820
then it must be wrong till the end.

756
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:19,840
That's what she owed me.

757
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:25,730
I'll trade!

758
00:40:26,480 --> 00:40:27,280
I'll trade.

759
00:40:32,360 --> 00:40:33,440
Mother was right.

760
00:40:34,670 --> 00:40:35,630
Nothing...

761
00:40:37,540 --> 00:40:39,070
can outweigh the An-Lu case

762
00:40:39,960 --> 00:40:41,400
in your heart.

763
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:53,710
Today, the entire Xie family is here.

764
00:40:53,710 --> 00:40:55,070
Please be my witnesses.

765
00:40:55,800 --> 00:40:57,860
Mother wrote a divorce paper long ago,

766
00:40:57,860 --> 00:40:59,720
and Father has agreed to it today.

767
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:00,460
From now on,

768
00:41:00,960 --> 00:41:04,160
Princess Yunzhao and the Xie family
have no further ties,

769
00:41:05,110 --> 00:41:06,170
parting amicably.

770
00:41:22,110 --> 00:41:23,070
Even if...

771
00:41:25,670 --> 00:41:27,670
you take Yunzhao away today,

772
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:32,060
without the Emperor and Empress Dowager
annulling the marriage,

773
00:41:32,680 --> 00:41:34,230
she, Li Fuhua,

774
00:41:35,030 --> 00:41:36,670
will always be my wife!

775
00:41:36,670 --> 00:41:37,550
Her soul will

776
00:41:37,920 --> 00:41:40,320
never leave the Xie ancestral hall!

777
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:46,680
You don't need to
worry about that, Father.

778
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:49,480
Father.

779
00:41:52,550 --> 00:41:54,880
This is the last time
I'll call you Father.

780
00:42:13,050 --> 00:42:19,000
♪ The past is dust,
we're passing through ♪

781
00:42:19,380 --> 00:42:24,750
♪ No regrets for what we've lost and won ♪

782
00:42:25,570 --> 00:42:31,000
♪ The shape of time begins to fade ♪

783
00:42:32,180 --> 00:42:37,000
♪ Half by choice, half washed away ♪

784
00:42:38,910 --> 00:42:43,840
♪ If fate is fragile,
what is right or wrong? ♪

785
00:42:45,320 --> 00:42:50,530
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

786
00:42:50,950 --> 00:42:54,510
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

787
00:42:54,530 --> 00:42:57,600
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

788
00:42:57,640 --> 00:43:03,020
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

789
00:42:59,460 --> 00:43:03,170
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

790
00:43:03,220 --> 00:43:07,290
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

791
00:43:07,320 --> 00:43:10,290
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

792
00:43:10,310 --> 00:43:17,060
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪
